331
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog čini ovakve čuda i dalje.

332
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog čini ovakve čude i dalje.

333
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:15,000
