337
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je vedno, Bog što radi dan danas.

338
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ako imamo petru.

339
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:40,000
